"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        ValidationInformation structures with different validation authority
        type fields.
        """
a = objects.ValidationInformation(validation_authority_type=enums.
    ValidationAuthorityType.COMMON_CRITERIA)
b = objects.ValidationInformation(validation_authority_type=enums.
    ValidationAuthorityType.UNSPECIFIED)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
